title: Make My Wish Come True
description: Happy Monday! As we get ready for Christmas this weekend we started with an all new Think Fast: Jenny vs Drake, a brand new Christmas Wish, Justin Bieber ticket giveaway, Checked in with everyone spouses with a Spouse Weekend X Factor, We tried our vocal chords to match Mariah Carey's Isolated Vocal Challenge, Singing our way through the show with Xmas songs, & More!
